name: Surprise CZ Pardon, Tempo’s $500M Raise, and More — Week in Review
description: Sinking into the volumetric wash of emergent capital, the Judge of Systems performs the solemn rite of collapse. Iridescent flocks of data-entropy burst from his chrome optics, signaling the chaotic rupture of known cycles and the violence of unexpected absolution.
